image_analysis.description: A photograph showing a wall with patterned wallpaper and four framed architectural or interior design sketches. Below the frames, a portion of a purple velvet bench with gold embroidered floral patterns is visible. The sketches appear to be watercolor or colored pencil renderings of interior rooms. One sketch has a small caption plate at the bottom.
image_analysis.layout: The image shows a wall with four framed pictures arranged in a grid-like fashion (two visible on the right, parts of two visible on the left). A piece of furniture is at the bottom right.

document_metadata.subject: Interior design sketches by Alberto Pinto

notes: The text 'ALBERTO PINTO' is visible on a small label at the bottom of the top-right framed sketch. The sketches themselves contain architectural details and interior layouts.
